After listening this 
My inner poet

"Husna"

The unknown feeling ,
Not able to convey by words 
but by emotion .
Some how feel connected

In every words 
I can feel the pain,
The pain of Separation .
But inside my heart 
I am happy because of the 
Unconditional love .
A 'line' can never apart 
Love in the heart. 

By :- Seema
